e, freedom","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadallah ibn \u2018Ubayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt is not permissible to jest about three matters: divorce, marriage, and emancipation.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 780 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33863,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/01\/khula-warning-divorce\/","url_meta":{"origin":13588,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Khula: Warning against initiating frivolous divorce","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf a woman asks her husband for a divorce without a strong reason, the fragrance of Paradise becomes forbidden for her.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2226 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062b\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2845,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/10\/allah-forgives-mistakes-coercion\/","url_meta":{"origin":13588,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Pardon: Allah forgives honest mistakes, coerced sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has pardoned my nation for their mistakes, their forgetfulness, and what they are coerced into doing.\u201d Source: Sunan\u00a0Ibn Ma\u0304jah 2043 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0630\u064e\u0631\u064d\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33879,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/06\/prophet-angered-by-triple-talaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":13588,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Divorce: The Prophet is angered by triple talaq","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Mahmud ibn Labid reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was informed about a man who pronounced divorce to his wife three times at once. The Prophe